title: Hunger
lyrics:
Looming threat
In my head
I found I’m in the thick of it
Forming threads
From my hands
Lead me back, I’ll follow it



I got my eyes on the horizon

I let the seed grow in my mouth



Bite my hunger

Let my mind, wild

In the Jungle, wild

Bite my hunger

Let my mind, ride

With the thunder, wild



Fell asleep

All a dream

Awoke to hear it calling me

Final leap

I’m on my feet

I’ve no idea where this will lead…



I got my eyes on the horizon

I let the seed grow in my mouth



Bite my hunger

Let my mind, wild

In the Jungle, wild

Bite my hunger

Let my mind, ride

With the thunder, wild



Forward

Homeward bound

Sink into

The Golden Hour
